                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h4>2018 - 2020</h4>
                        <p>Full-Stack Developer, built core infrastructure and payment systems processing $100M+ in transactions.</p>
